---
title: Home
layout: main
isPage: true
---
  
header
  h1 Welcome to my blog
  p I write about development and all kinds of tech stuff that I get my hands on. Keep in touch!

each post in getCollection("posts").toJSON()
  section
    h2
      a(href=post.url)= post.title
    .post-metadata  
      span On 
        != post.date.toDateString()
      .tags
        span in
        ul
          //- List tags with links in a comma separated list (no comma after last tag)
          each tag, index in post.tags
            li
              a(href='tags/'+tag)= tag
              if(index < post.tags.length-1)
                ,

    p= post.summary

